data.description: **1 YEAR RATE BUY DOWN** with acceptable offer!!!  How does 4.5% sound??  $28,000 savings...This exquisite home has been thoughtfully upgraded throughout, offering both style and functionality. Here's a detailed list of the impressive features:Crown Molding: Crown molding graces the entire house, adding a touch of elegance to each room.Plantation Shutters: Enjoy privacy and sophistication in the office, library, and master bedroom with custom plantation shutters.Pella Windows and Doors: High-quality Pella windows and doors enhance energy efficiency and provide a sleek, modern aesthetic.Beamed Ceiling: The great room and kitchen feature stunning beamed ceilings, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere.Hardwood and Tile Floors: Throughout the home, you'll find beautiful hardwood and tile floors that are both durable and easy to maintain.Fireplaces: Cozy up with a gas fireplace in the great room and a wood-burning fireplace on the covered porch, perfect for year-round relaxation.Handmade Features: Handcrafted maple floating shelves and mantles for both fireplaces showcase the attention to detail in this home.Three-Season Enclosed Porch: Enjoy the outdoors in comfort with a three-season enclosed covered porch.Ceiling Fans: Ceiling fans are installed throughout the house for added comfort and energy efficiency.Tiled Baths: All baths feature tiled surfaces, with the master bath boasting a double shower head for a luxurious experience.Tray Ceilings: The entry and office feature tray ceilings, adding architectural interest to these spaces.Professional Closet Systems: All closets have been professionally designed and organized by Closet Solutions.Gourmet Kitchen: The kitchen is a chef's dream, with a Miele built-in coffee maker, a Blue Star gas range, a Blue Star built-in electric oven with a pizza stone, a built-in microwave, quartz countertops, and an island for meal preparation.Granite Countertops: The rest of the home features granite countertops, adding a touch of luxury.Pass-Thru Pantry: The pass-thru pantry includes a sink, a second refrigerator, and ample cabinet space for storage and convenience.Laundry Room: The laundry room features a stainless steel dog washing station, making pet care a breeze.Built-In Office Cabinets: At the garage entry, you'll find built-in office cabinets, wall lockers, and a shoe rack for efficient organization.Cedar-Lined Closets: Enjoy the benefits of cedar-lined storage closets, which provide a fresh and pleasant aroma.Upgraded Cabinets: The kitchen and master bath cabinets have been upgraded for both style and functionality.Oversized Three-Car Garage: The spacious three-car garage offers ample room for vehicles and storage.Second-Floor Gym: Stay fit and healthy with a dedicated gym on the second floor, featuring rubber flooring.Barn Doors: The fourth bedroom is adorned with handcrafted barn doors, adding a rustic charm.Front Door: A stunning oversized double front door with opening windows and screens makes a grand entrance.Under Counter Lighting and Plugs: Convenient under-counter lighting and plugs add functionality to the kitchen.Sealed Crawl Space: The sealed crawl space ensures the home is well-maintained and energy-efficient.These upgrades combine to create a truly exceptional living experience in this beautiful home. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours!
